cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.DS 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper is about intrusion detection system for enterprise security. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a graph-based approach that leverages random walk technique to measure the anomaly score of process paths. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the Box-Cox power transformation based approach is introduced to normalize the anomaly scores. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the implementation and deployment of the proposed algorithm in a real enterprise security system. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also a possible category as the paper proposes an optimization scheme to improve the efficiency of suspicious path discovery.
